{"id":294548,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/维权网-江苏上访维权人士张玲拘留期满获释/","date":"2013-05-21T18:16:15Z","modified":"2013-05-21T18:16:15Z","title":"维权网 | 江苏上访维权人士张玲拘留期满获释","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员疾风报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>江苏省江阴市访民张玲遭到江阴市公安局以到北京非正常上访，“扰乱了公共场所秩序”为理由行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>点半</span><span>，张玲从江阴市拘留所获释，回到家中。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，张玲，女，现年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">44</span><span>岁，家住江阴市长山渡江二村</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>幢</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">301</span><span>室。原是江阴市东辰机械制造有限公司业务员，该公司拖欠她四年的辛辛苦苦劳动所得的血汗钱六十多万元，江阴法院权钱交易，生效判决六年不执行。无奈之下，张玲只好到北京上访，讨要劳动报酬，不想劳动报酬没有讨到，却因此多次遭到当地政府打压，被拘留，关黑监狱等。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日，张玲又到北京上访，揭露江阴市公、检、法各级机徇私枉法、钱权交易等违法行径。在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日，两次被北京警察关马家楼。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>，张玲被江阴市警方从马家楼强制带回当地并传唤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>，张玲遭刑事逼供后，被江阴市公安局处以行政处罚拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张玲手机：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18626057108</span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}